content: No. 23 Virginia Tech returns to the road for Thursday tilt at Syracuse  VT hokiesports.com
description: The Virginia Tech women's basketball team (19-6, 11-3) returns to the court on Thursday evening when they take on the Syracuse Orange (11-13, 4-10).
